              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The cross sections of monitor reaction were determined",
                "by interpolation of the evaluated values of the",
                "reference as \"Physik Daten - Physics Data, Evaluation",
                "of Cross Sections for 14 Important Neutron-Dosimetry",
                "Reactions. Fachinformationszentrum Karlsruhe,",
                "Gesellschaft fur wissenschaftlich-technische",
                "Information mbH, Federal Republic of Germany,",
                "No. 13-5 (1990)\"."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The tritium-titanium (T-Ti) target used in the",
                "generator was 2.18 mg/cm2 thick. The effective source",
                "neutron energy at irradiation position was determined",
                "by the Nb/Zr method, and the uncertainty in the",
                "neutron energy at around 3 to 5 cm was estimated to",
                "be 200 keV from a consideration of the sample sizes,",
                "beam diameter of about 3-4 mm, and the uncertainty in",
                "the Nb/Zr method."
              ]
            }
          ],
